olved satellite ``Dysnomea'' which\nmay contribute for $\\approx0.02$ mag to the total brightness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Oct 2006 10:23:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
